      public void insertMultipleResources​(java.util.List<Resource> resources, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> shelves) throws IllegalShelfException

      Parameters:

      shelves - List of Integer which represents for each resource the shelf where it has to be inserted

    • checkInsertMultipleRes

      public boolean checkInsertMultipleRes​(java.util.List<Resource> resources, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> shelves)
      This method checks if the resources passed ad parameters can be inserted in the Warehouse
      Parameters:
      resources - List of resources which indicates all the resources that should be inserted
      shelves - List of integers which represents for each resource the shelf in which the resource should be inserted
      Returns:
      true if the resources can be inserted, false otherwise
